Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来一发射线喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这射线真是越发性感了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}白色月姬  Phantas  Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic  Circuit  Fullcount  大回转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marble  Phantasm！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绅士怪人  松旺子武君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又遇到了大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被嫉妒所附体的妖怪赤发女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy85\fscx85\pos(416,330)}秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然开始将锅子当成化妆品来卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再来花言巧语了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此刻出现了意外的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  莲  你要拿那蒟蒻干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  白色月姬  Phantas  Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行政改革
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也要让你的心Marble  Phantasm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法少女题材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人类少女的时光只不过是一瞬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}心跳！Melty  Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野君  这是速食咖喱  而且里面还是冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要让大脑得到休息的话  放松是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和哥哥在海边…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵先生  要麦茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵少爷  这样下去皮肤会「把」太阳晒伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哈哈哈  该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是养眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  虽然是来玩  但你好歹是远野家长男  像样点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.07,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}私人海滩  闲人免进  远野家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里之后你就一直在傻笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有在想奇怪的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我放手你这笨蛋吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的啊  放手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日特别企划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野家主办  心跳沙滩排球大会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那啥啊志贵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天啊  夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女佣也不再是女佣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了我也「被」女仆装脱掉  变回女人的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为各位的心都生锈了  所以才要用运动来加深感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  把球砸进对方的领地里就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道沙滩排球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发球的台词是Potemkin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分之后是Gal  Undo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以教坏别人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是玩  小规则就不用在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就来抽签分成两组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜的一队有优胜团体奖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有个人奖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\1c&000000&\shad0\fs17\fscx80\pos(480,250)}优胜队伍  秋田小町米一年份\N最佳射手奖  鬼战车  T-34\N沙滩女王奖  碗刷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这次的MVP可以得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供和志贵先生在单间一起过夜的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  琥珀  这种没羞耻的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为各种失误  食物和房间都只预定了一份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在赶快去重新准备  如果出什么事就太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动万能的秋叶小姐只要拿到MVP就能保住志贵先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你成为MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有两人还是有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这种事  我很开心哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我必须得做点什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没没什么啊  哦呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就开始抽签分队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}白队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  居然和雪儿一起  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要敬谢不敏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外…外国人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了  都古小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱味好重  这个是印度人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}红队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心  我会「被」加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最佳阵容  根据我的计算  败率是0
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为能接下我的发球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potemkin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gal  Undo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹扣杀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  球还没出界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笑纳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都古小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在拳上看到怎样的将来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父！

Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气真背
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪儿快看  球还没出界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  接给你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVP  MVP  MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了  反射性地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gal  Undo！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止都还在计算之内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么计算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一口气决定胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里门顶肘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才修好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止都还在计算之内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪儿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该来个大招了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这根本就是犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gal  Undo！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  人外们的血战还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是人外！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…525比526…
